MUF (programming language), or "Multi-User Forth", a Forth derivative used in TinyMUCK and descendants

wiki.text:
'muf' is a collaborative of artists, architects and urban designers based in
London, England, specialising in the design of the urban public realm to
facilitate appropriation by users.
